:: Rejection target: the reduction right-hand side introduces the free pattern
:: variable `y` that does not occur in the left-hand side. Spec 17.6.4 rule 1
:: requires every free RHS pattern variable to occur free in the LHS
:: (doc/spec/en/17.clusters_and_registrations.md, section 17.6.4, rule 1).

definition
  let x be set;
  func TagDef: tag(x) -> set equals [x];
end;

registration
  let x, y be set;

  reduce TagFresh: tag(x) to [y];
  reducibility proof thus thesis; end;
end;
